{
  "stem": "5799.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But if they were told to give you-- to give lists, they should have forewarned the people, knocked at every door, and said look.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I'm giving them the list, because I have to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But you run, and try to save yourself, because you know what it is for.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after we were in the ghetto, I lived through two executions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "One, I was left to live, because we were childrens-- children of professionals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The second execution was in the summer of '42, where I decided that I do not exist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I will not register with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I will not have them a number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because if I'll run someplace, they can not take revenge over my parents or my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So I used to take her number, but I didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I only had the yellow-- the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I worked on the cemetery-- on the old German cemetery in Novogrudok.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But actually, we dug graves, and planted the Impatiens, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I had a grave by a German who got killed-- [LAUGHS] --in 1917.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "His name was William Loch And every day, I hung my little jacket over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We had very few clothing at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I used to say a prayer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Thank you, William Loch, that you died in the first world war, otherwise you would be here now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So it's one less.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was my prayer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I didn't pray much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I was angry with God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I thought he was a sadist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I could forgive him everything but the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I used to say, how could you sit there and watch babies being killed?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did they ever do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was always that debate between me and the unknown.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
